From: =?UTF-8?q?Timur=20Krist=C3=B3f?= <timur.kristof@gmail.com>
Date: Mon, 25 Aug 2025 23:56:30 +0200
Subject: [PATCH] drm/amd/display: Disable VRR on DCE 6
Mime-version: 1.0
Content-type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-transfer-encoding: 8bit
Git-commit: 043c87d7d56e135393f8aab927148096e2d17589
Patch-mainline: v6.18-rc1
References: stable-fixes

DCE 6 was not advertised as being able to support VRR,
so let's mark it as unsupported for now.

The VRR implementation in amdgpu_dm depends on the VUPDATE
interrupt which is not registered for DCE 6.

Signed-off-by: Timur Krist√≥f <timur.kristof@gmail.com>
Reviewed-by: Rodrigo Siqueira <siqueira@igalia.com>
Reviewed-by: Alex Deucher <alexander.deucher@amd.com>
Reviewed-by: Alex Hung <alex.hung@amd.com>
Signed-off-by: Alex Deucher <alexander.deucher@amd.com>
Acked-by: Takashi Iwai <tiwai@suse.de>

---
 drivers/gpu/drm/amd/display/amdgpu_dm/amdgpu_dm.c |    4 +++-
 drivers/gpu/drm/amd/display/dc/dc_helper.c        |    5 +++++
 drivers/gpu/drm/amd/display/dc/dm_services.h      |    2 ++
 3 files changed, 10 insertions(+), 1 deletion(-)

--- a/drivers/gpu/drm/amd/display/amdgpu_dm/amdgpu_dm.c
+++ b/drivers/gpu/drm/amd/display/amdgpu_dm/amdgpu_dm.c
@@ -10537,6 +10537,8 @@ static void get_freesync_config_for_crtc
 		} else {
 			config.state = VRR_STATE_INACTIVE;
 		}
+	} else {
+		config.state = VRR_STATE_UNSUPPORTED;
 	}
 out:
 	new_crtc_state->freesync_config = config;
@@ -12439,7 +12441,7 @@ void amdgpu_dm_update_freesync_caps(stru
 
 	dm_con_state = to_dm_connector_state(connector->state);
 
-	if (!adev->dm.freesync_module)
+	if (!adev->dm.freesync_module || !dc_supports_vrr(sink->ctx->dce_version))
 		goto update;
 
 	/* Some eDP panels only have the refresh rate range info in DisplayID */
--- a/drivers/gpu/drm/amd/display/dc/dc_helper.c
+++ b/drivers/gpu/drm/amd/display/dc/dc_helper.c
@@ -747,3 +747,8 @@ char *dce_version_to_string(const int ve
 		return "Unknown";
 	}
 }
+
+bool dc_supports_vrr(const enum dce_version v)
+{
+	return v >= DCE_VERSION_8_0;
+}
--- a/drivers/gpu/drm/amd/display/dc/dm_services.h
+++ b/drivers/gpu/drm/amd/display/dc/dm_services.h
@@ -304,4 +304,6 @@ void dm_dtn_log_end(struct dc_context *c
 
 char *dce_version_to_string(const int version);
 
+bool dc_supports_vrr(const enum dce_version v);
+
 #endif /* __DM_SERVICES_H__ */
